Which network- related tool combines elements of both ping and traceroute?
A)  tcpdump
B)  wireshark
C)  mtr
D)  nmcli
C
C. The mtr command combines elements of both ping and traceroute. Among the othercommands, nmcli is the NetworkManagement manage tool for network. Both tcpdumpand wireshark/tshark are used for monitoring the network.
